comments:
Created 1.4.1899 out of the parish of Kirkleatham. Abolished 1.4.1921 
    and added to the parish of Redcar.

That part which until 1.4.1921 formed part of the parish of Wilton. See 
    also Table 2, note (b).

That part which until 1.4.1934 formed part of the parish of 
    Easington. See also Table 2, note (e).

Created 1894 from the part of the parish of Marske in Saltburn 
    by the Sea Urban District. See also Table 2, note (d).
